231
00:13:38.562 --> 00:13:38.762
for

232
00:13:39.762 --> 00:13:43.082
them 50 years after they've been generated.

233
00:13:43.842 --> 00:13:47.162
And of course, they're also responsible directly for the

234
00:13:47.202 --> 00:13:49.842
